	&lt;/ol&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;add a helper method to unify (correct) cleanup so that if an exception is thrown in the `finally` block, it will be added as a suppressed exception&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;ol&gt;
